If you have eaten the LantChips , there is no way that they are the best as a group; the Kettle chips are rightly salted and I was so irritated by some Pringles products. Kettle has good flavor but the small size and oiliness takes away from its appeal. All in all, its good to have choice--Amazon does not stock the best product all the time so there are some days that there is no choice.

If you love hot sauce..I mean really love hot sauce, but don't want a sauce that tastelessly burns your throat, grab a bottle of Tequila Picante Gourmet de Inclan. Just realize that once you taste it, you will never want to use any other sauce.

Thank you for the personal, incredible
